cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with image segmentation. The use of deep learning models also suggests that it could belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI) categories. The introduction of a novel convolution module indicates that it could also belong to the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) category. Finally, the use of electron microscopy images suggests that it could belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) category.
